org.apache.flink.api.common.io.compression

接口 InflaterInputStreamFactory<T extends InflaterInputStream>

  • 所有已知实现类:
    DeflateInflaterInputStreamFactory, GzipInflaterInputStreamFactory

    @Internal
public interface InflaterInputStreamFactory<T extends InflaterInputStream>
    Creates a new instance of a certain subclass of InflaterInputStream.

    • 方法概要

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      T create(InputStream in)
      Creates a InflaterInputStream that wraps the given input stream.
      Collection<String> getCommonFileExtensions()
      Lists a collection of typical file extensions (e.g., "gz", "gzip") that are associated with the compression algorithm in the InflaterInputStream T.

    • 方法详细资料

      • create

        T create(InputStream in)
  throws IOException
        Creates a InflaterInputStream that wraps the given input stream.
        参数:
        in - is the compressed input stream
        返回:
        the inflated input stream
        抛出:
        IOException

      • getCommonFileExtensions

        Collection<String> getCommonFileExtensions()
        Lists a collection of typical file extensions (e.g., "gz", "gzip") that are associated with the compression algorithm in the InflaterInputStream T.
        返回:
        a (possibly empty) collection of lower-case file extensions, without the period
